OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening and overnight with further
OL,7,Fspells of rain or showers. Showers
OL,8,Fheavy at times and merging into longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain. Generally light winds
OL,10,Fand slightly chillier than previous
OL,11,Fnights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA damp morning with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain. Turning drier
OL,15,Fthrough the afternoon with a few
OL,16,Fshowers mixed with sunny spells later.
OL,17,FSomewhat less mild but winds generally
OL,18,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
