OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDamp
OL,6,Fand windier on Sunday with periods of
OL,7,Fdrizzly rain, this mostly over the
OL,8,Fhills. Generally drier on Monday but
OL,9,Fshowery rain still possible. Perhaps
OL,10,Fbrighter on Tuesday. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
